"aim_bunk3rs" by: Myke, tpskjarhead. This is a map I, Myke, originally designed and modeled with Google SketchUp. It has three (3) war bunkers, hense the name "bunk3rs", pretty creative, I know. Features: 24 Spawn Points Total. Buy Zones Lighting Swimming Fish High Quality Sounds. [Roof walking, wall shots, etc.] Credits: Modeled with Google SketchUp, and designed originally by: Myke. Finished, and mapped by: tpskjarhead.
The screen shots are on "low" quality setting, actually in-game play, is higher quality, and a lot more realistic.
